query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(t mi) NoHashJoin(mi t it) NoMergeJoin(it mi t mc) NoNestLoop(it mc mi t ct) */ select min(t.title) AS typical_european_movie
from title AS t
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Norway',
'Norwegian',
'USA',
'Danish',
'Bulgaria',
'American',
'Denish',
'Swedish')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.note like '%(theatrical)%' AND mc.note like '%(France)%'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies';
